### Health API
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Seed rules via CLI
# run in terminal: seed-rules

### Simulator pending orders (external API)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/orders?status=READY_FOR_ENRICHMENT&limit=20

### Submit enrichment payload example
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/orders/ORD-20260307-000123/enrichment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "correlation_id": "9d1d2c9f-9c5f-4f1a-8e3e-111111111111",
  "source_system": "rules-enrichment-daemon",
  "enrichment_version": 1,
  "applied_rules": [
    {
      "rule_id": "RULE-DEST-ES-001",
      "rule_type": "destination",
      "description": "Destination country is ES"
    }
  ],
  "enriched_fields": {
    "destination_lane": "ES01",
    "source_handling_code": "SPECIAL_ORIGIN",
    "treatment_code": "STANDARD",
    "allocation_zone": "A1"
  }
}
